ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 173 - (Manitoba) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 173 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING which caused damage to private property, small businesses, farms and infrastructure from April 28 to June 4, 2013.
